com.github.crashdemons.mobeggdrops.api

Interface EggType


  • public interface EggType
    Object representing the type of Head supported by PlayerHeads. You can obtain the headtype for various things through API methods - to compare head types, you can use equals()
    Author:
    crashdemons (crashenator at gmail.com)
